1
00:01:41,630 --> 00:01:46,000
[Love of the Divine Tree]

2
00:01:46,680 --> 00:01:48,940
[Episode 6]

3
00:01:58,360 --> 00:01:59,610
Why?

4
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:03,460
Why do you always make decisions on your own?

5
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:05,230
You don't trust me,

6
00:02:05,510 --> 00:02:07,440
yet why do you take the blame for me?

7
00:02:08,979 --> 00:02:10,710
Just because you're my master,

8
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:12,030
you think you can say nothing

9
00:02:12,030 --> 00:02:12,960
and die for me?

10
00:02:23,320 --> 00:02:24,980
Using your death to punish me,

11
00:02:27,240 --> 00:02:29,100
is this your way of being a master?

12
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:34,630
Master.

13
00:02:47,520 --> 00:02:49,329
You can't just end it this way.

14
00:02:49,850 --> 00:02:51,780
I will never accept your kindness.

15
00:02:52,940 --> 00:02:54,800
Even if I have to tear down the sky,

16
00:02:54,840 --> 00:02:56,430
I'll bring you back to life.

17
00:02:58,520 --> 00:02:59,750
I'll pay

18
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:01,190
my own debt.

19
00:03:02,280 --> 00:03:03,240
What I owe you,

20
00:03:04,240 --> 00:03:05,900
I'll definitely pay you back.

21
00:03:20,800 --> 00:03:21,690
Master.

22
00:03:30,070 --> 00:03:31,630
Mu Qingge!

23
00:04:24,240 --> 00:04:24,830
Yishui!

24
00:04:26,120 --> 00:04:26,950
Su Yishui!

25
00:04:30,680 --> 00:04:31,310
Su Yishui!

26
00:04:35,480 --> 00:04:36,040
Yishui.

27
00:04:36,950 --> 00:04:37,870
I can

28
00:04:38,360 --> 00:04:39,690
let bygones be bygones.

29
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:40,950
Did Mu Qingge

30
00:04:41,390 --> 00:04:42,090
tell you

31
00:04:42,120 --> 00:04:44,250
the whereabouts of the Spirit Spring?

32
00:04:46,750 --> 00:04:49,010
We still have a chance to turn the tables.

33
00:04:49,680 --> 00:04:50,270
Yishui,

34
00:04:51,140 --> 00:04:52,940
you are still the Demon's child.

35
00:04:53,240 --> 00:04:54,120
As long as you're willing,

36
00:04:54,120 --> 00:04:54,800
we can

37
00:04:54,830 --> 00:04:55,740
find the Spirit Spring again

38
00:04:55,740 --> 00:04:57,200
and reclaim the universe.

39
00:04:57,230 --> 00:04:58,750
Leading the entire universe,

40
00:04:58,750 --> 00:05:00,150
isn't that what you want?

41
00:05:11,240 --> 00:05:12,310
Su Yishui!

42
00:05:56,950 --> 00:05:57,990
You, an immortal master of the mortal world,

43
00:05:57,990 --> 00:06:00,250
are becoming increasingly outrageous.

44
00:06:00,480 --> 00:06:01,870
You stole the Ice Lotus before

45
00:06:01,870 --> 00:06:03,160
and chased away the guardian cat.

46
00:06:03,160 --> 00:06:04,800
Today you broke into my cave.

47
00:06:05,020 --> 00:06:07,350
Do you no longer care for your mortal body?

48
00:06:07,390 --> 00:06:08,390
I, Su Yishui,

49
00:06:09,080 --> 00:06:10,160
beg you to grant me the Reincarnation Tree

50
00:06:10,160 --> 00:06:11,160
to save my master.

51
00:06:11,160 --> 00:06:13,430
The Reincarnation Tree is such a divine object.

52
00:06:13,430 --> 00:06:15,270
You're just an immortal master of the mortal world.

53
00:06:15,270 --> 00:06:16,830
You can't just simply ask for it.

54
00:06:16,830 --> 00:06:17,960
I beg for your mercy.

55
00:06:30,190 --> 00:06:31,550
The Reincarnation Tree

56
00:06:31,570 --> 00:06:33,270
is right behind the Thousand Light Beams.

57
00:06:33,270 --> 00:06:35,670
Let's see if you can risk your life to get it.

58
00:11:58,390 --> 00:11:59,000
Su Yishui.

59
00:12:00,790 --> 00:12:01,390
Su Yishui.

60
00:12:10,720 --> 00:12:11,360
Su Yishui.

61
00:12:11,980 --> 00:12:12,960
Even if you risked your life

62
00:12:12,960 --> 00:12:14,150
to get the Reincarnation Tree,

63
00:12:14,150 --> 00:12:14,870
it would not be enough

64
00:12:14,870 --> 00:12:17,470
to compensate for the kindness you owe Master.

65
00:12:25,210 --> 00:12:26,270
It has borne fruit.

66
00:12:46,870 --> 00:12:47,720
These two

67
00:12:48,360 --> 00:12:49,690
are Master and Mu Ranwu.

68
00:12:50,200 --> 00:12:51,260
But why did Mu Ranwu

69
00:12:51,630 --> 00:12:52,870
have to rush into the formation at the end

70
00:12:52,870 --> 00:12:53,870
and lose her life?

71
00:12:54,440 --> 00:12:55,770
She was insignificant,

72
00:12:56,840 --> 00:12:58,920
but under the Empyrean Bone Sacrifice Curse,

73
00:12:58,920 --> 00:13:00,040
their souls were shattered

74
00:13:00,040 --> 00:13:01,170
and mixed together.

75
00:13:02,030 --> 00:13:04,090
They can only be reborn together now.

76
00:13:08,150 --> 00:13:10,080
When will Master be able to return?

77
00:13:12,670 --> 00:13:14,670
The Reincarnation Tree defies the heavens.

78
00:13:14,670 --> 00:13:16,800
It will take 18 years for her to return.

79
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:20,510
You're so severely injured.

80
00:13:20,510 --> 00:13:23,010
You need to go into seclusion to preserve your life.

81
00:13:23,010 --> 00:13:23,790
During these 18 years,

82
00:13:23,790 --> 00:13:24,990
if anything happens,

83
00:13:25,290 --> 00:13:26,690
how will you protect her?

84
00:13:28,720 --> 00:13:29,720
I have my own ways.

85
00:13:36,240 --> 00:13:38,900
Why are you extracting your own spiritual soul?

86
00:13:55,830 --> 00:13:57,960
The Reincarnation Tree absorbs the Golden Core,

87
00:13:57,960 --> 00:13:59,360
using the soul as a guide.

88
00:13:59,480 --> 00:14:01,960
After this, I will seclude myself and lose all five senses.

89
00:14:01,960 --> 00:14:03,620
This part of my spiritual soul

90
00:14:04,150 --> 00:14:05,480
can accompany her.

91
00:14:17,510 --> 00:14:19,270
You've also placed a restriction on her appearance.

92
00:14:19,270 --> 00:14:20,400
After she is reborn,

93
00:14:20,910 --> 00:14:22,000
what everyone sees

94
00:14:22,510 --> 00:14:24,480
will no longer be Mu Qingge's appearance.

95
00:14:24,480 --> 00:14:25,220
This time,

96
00:14:25,940 --> 00:14:26,670
I absolutely won't

97
00:14:26,670 --> 00:14:28,530
let worldly affairs disturb her.

98
00:14:36,840 --> 00:14:37,630
Su Yishui,

99
00:14:38,440 --> 00:14:40,000
when you eliminated Mu Qingge,

100
00:14:40,000 --> 00:14:41,390
the barrier you raised

101
00:14:41,790 --> 00:14:42,520
was actually

102
00:14:42,540 --> 00:14:44,580
to collect her remaining soul.

103
00:14:46,400 --> 00:14:47,240
Why did you give up

104
00:14:47,240 --> 00:14:49,390
the Transcendence Realm that was within your grasp

105
00:14:49,390 --> 00:14:50,550
and use half a Golden Core

106
00:14:50,550 --> 00:14:52,010
to reincarnate Mu Qingge?

107
00:14:54,150 --> 00:14:55,210
To break the curse.

108
00:14:55,630 --> 00:14:57,510
Besides the Face-and-Heart Burning Curse,

109
00:14:57,510 --> 00:14:59,570
Mu Qingge also placed another curse.

110
00:14:59,720 --> 00:15:00,300
It was to

111
00:15:00,320 --> 00:15:01,920
tie the lifeline of Mount Wester's disciples

112
00:15:01,920 --> 00:15:02,870
to her own.

113
00:15:03,320 --> 00:15:04,550
If she dies tragically,

114
00:15:04,550 --> 00:15:05,320
the descendants of Mount Wester

115
00:15:05,320 --> 00:15:07,720
will suffer the same fate for generations.

116
00:15:09,320 --> 00:15:10,480
Your Mount Wester

117
00:15:10,510 --> 00:15:12,200
has only a few dozen people.

118
00:15:12,320 --> 00:15:14,620
How can you risk the lives of all people for them?

119
00:15:14,620 --> 00:15:15,570
After Mu Qingge's death,

120
00:15:15,570 --> 00:15:17,000
the Spirit Spring's whereabouts became unknown.

121
00:15:17,000 --> 00:15:19,730
Don't you want to find the Spirit Spring anymore?

122
00:15:22,280 --> 00:15:23,920
If you don't agree,

123
00:15:32,610 --> 00:15:33,670
then I will fight to the death

124
00:15:33,670 --> 00:15:34,730
against all of you.

125
00:15:40,480 --> 00:15:41,550
In 18 years,

126
00:15:41,750 --> 00:15:43,910
Immortal Kaiyuan, you will face the heavenly tribulation.

127
00:15:43,910 --> 00:15:45,440
If Mu Qingge reincarnates,

128
00:15:45,480 --> 00:15:47,070
she can break the curse on Mount Wester

129
00:15:47,070 --> 00:15:49,330
and help you withstand the tribulation.

130
00:15:49,720 --> 00:15:51,380
Do you want to risk death today

131
00:15:51,660 --> 00:15:53,570
or fight for survival in 18 years?

132
00:15:55,620 --> 00:15:56,370
Fine.

133
00:16:00,790 --> 00:16:02,360
Heaven values all life.

134
00:16:02,820 --> 00:16:04,270
I'll agree to your request.

135
00:16:04,270 --> 00:16:05,690
We'll leave this Reincarnation Tree.

136
00:16:05,690 --> 00:16:07,980
When the Reincarnation Tree bears fruit in 18 years,

137
00:16:07,980 --> 00:16:10,380
we will come back to personally oversee it.

138
00:16:10,480 --> 00:16:12,600
Even if Mu Qingge can reincarnate,

139
00:16:12,720 --> 00:16:14,910
we won't give her any chance to do evil.

140
00:16:43,200 --> 00:16:44,130
In 18 years,

141
00:16:45,390 --> 00:16:46,720
I'll come to pick you up.

142
00:16:51,790 --> 00:16:53,600
You're already at the end of your rope.

143
00:16:53,600 --> 00:16:55,720
Why don't you go into seclusion quickly?

144
00:16:55,720 --> 00:16:58,250
There's one more thing she entrusted me with.

145
00:16:59,220 --> 00:17:00,660
[Wangxiang Pass, Cave]

146
00:17:24,200 --> 00:17:26,710
I originally wanted to seal the Spirit Spring back in the netherworld,

147
00:17:26,710 --> 00:17:27,680
but I found out

148
00:17:28,280 --> 00:17:29,440
only the Demon's child at the stage of Transcendence

149
00:17:29,440 --> 00:17:30,160
could do it.

150
00:17:30,960 --> 00:17:32,640
I could only exhaust my Golden Core

151
00:17:32,640 --> 00:17:35,590
to temporarily seal this source of all demons in the mortal world.

152
00:17:35,590 --> 00:17:36,510
Su Yishui,

153
00:17:37,070 --> 00:17:37,730
if you still

154
00:17:37,750 --> 00:17:39,480
have a sense of gratitude to me,

155
00:17:40,110 --> 00:17:41,570
just promise me one thing.

156
00:17:42,160 --> 00:17:44,350
I've sealed the Spirit Spring at Wangxiang Pass.

157
00:17:44,350 --> 00:17:46,750
Please return it to the netherworld for me.

158
00:17:48,920 --> 00:17:50,310
Where's the Spirit Spring?

159
00:17:50,310 --> 00:17:52,480
Master said she sealed the Spirit Spring here.

160
00:17:52,480 --> 00:17:53,440
Why is it gone?

161
00:17:56,590 --> 00:17:57,520
Are you alright?

162
00:18:03,400 --> 00:18:04,030
I can't sense

163
00:18:04,030 --> 00:18:05,630
any trace of demonic energy.

164
00:18:06,550 --> 00:18:07,270
This indicates that the Spirit Spring

165
00:18:07,270 --> 00:18:08,530
is still well-sealed.

166
00:18:09,040 --> 00:18:10,030
For some unknown reason,

167
00:18:10,030 --> 00:18:11,290
it has been relocated.

168
00:18:13,240 --> 00:18:14,500
In your current state,

169
00:18:14,650 --> 00:18:15,310
you'd better

170
00:18:15,310 --> 00:18:16,880
go into seclusion and recuperate.

171
00:18:16,880 --> 00:18:18,480
Don't end up losing your life

172
00:18:18,510 --> 00:18:20,030
without finding the Spirit Spring.

173
00:18:20,030 --> 00:18:20,680
After 18 years,

174
00:18:20,680 --> 00:18:22,280
how will you protect Master?

175
00:18:27,670 --> 00:18:31,040
[Mount Wester]

176
00:18:43,400 --> 00:18:45,020
With this Reincarnation Tree,

177
00:18:45,020 --> 00:18:46,680
you still need to use half a Golden Core

178
00:18:46,680 --> 00:18:48,310
and a fraction of your spiritual soul as a guide

179
00:18:48,310 --> 00:18:50,240
to ensure her safe reincarnation.

180
00:18:50,350 --> 00:18:51,750
Do you know that?

181
00:18:51,920 --> 00:18:53,920
I'm willing to do whatever it takes.

182
00:18:53,960 --> 00:18:55,920
But are you willing to

183
00:18:56,070 --> 00:18:57,200
fail her final wish?

184
00:18:58,000 --> 00:19:00,070
Only the Demon's child at the stage of Transcendence

185
00:19:00,070 --> 00:19:02,440
can seal the Spirit Spring back into the netherworld.

186
00:19:02,440 --> 00:19:04,640
But with only nine-tenths of your spiritual sense remaining,

187
00:19:04,640 --> 00:19:07,410
you'll never be able to advance to the stage of Transcendence.

188
00:19:07,410 --> 00:19:09,200
Reviving her or fulfilling her wish,

189
00:19:09,200 --> 00:19:10,750
you can only choose one.

190
00:19:19,240 --> 00:19:21,480
I beg you to grant me a way to achieve both.

191
00:19:21,480 --> 00:19:23,070
A way to achieve both

192
00:19:23,120 --> 00:19:25,400
is nothing more than a temporary solution

193
00:19:25,400 --> 00:19:27,720
in exchange for your suffering.

194
00:19:29,030 --> 00:19:29,790
Please.

195
00:19:32,250 --> 00:19:34,010
My twelve-petaled Ice Lotus

196
00:19:34,030 --> 00:19:35,340
is the purest.

197
00:19:35,640 --> 00:19:38,030
If you use the Ice Lotus to complete the incomplete core,

198
00:19:38,030 --> 00:19:40,770
you should be able to regain the power of Transcendence.

199
00:19:40,770 --> 00:19:42,440
However, to incorporate the Ice Lotus into your technique,

200
00:19:42,440 --> 00:19:44,350
you must cultivate it without emotions.

201
00:19:44,350 --> 00:19:46,270
Otherwise, when your seven emotions are disturbed,

202
00:19:46,270 --> 00:19:47,960
the technique will backfire.

203
00:19:48,240 --> 00:19:49,540
If you experience extreme emotions,

204
00:19:49,540 --> 00:19:50,880
or give up completely to natural impulse,

205
00:19:50,880 --> 00:19:52,510
causing the Ice Lotus Technique to break,

206
00:19:52,510 --> 00:19:54,510
you'll suffer extreme pain.

207
00:19:54,880 --> 00:19:55,550
And then

208
00:19:55,830 --> 00:19:57,830
you'll lose the power of Transcendence.

209
00:19:57,830 --> 00:19:59,890
If you still want to fulfill her wish,

210
00:19:59,920 --> 00:20:01,240
you can only do so

211
00:20:01,270 --> 00:20:04,130
by sacrificing your life to seal the Spirit Spring.

212
00:20:07,310 --> 00:20:08,030
I won't go down

213
00:20:08,030 --> 00:20:09,290
such a desperate path.

214
00:20:09,400 --> 00:20:10,720
Hopefully not.

215
00:20:11,160 --> 00:20:12,070
Remember,

216
00:20:12,240 --> 00:20:13,030
in the future,

217
00:20:13,030 --> 00:20:15,030
Mu Qingge will be a brand new person,

218
00:20:15,120 --> 00:20:16,930
and you, Su Yishui,

219
00:20:16,960 --> 00:20:18,420
will become emotionless.

220
00:21:20,310 --> 00:21:21,550
When you return

221
00:21:22,270 --> 00:21:23,680
in 18 years,

222
00:21:24,550 --> 00:21:26,240
no one will be able to hurt you.

223
00:21:31,930 --> 00:21:36,110
[18 years later]
[Xue Village near Mount Absolute]

224
00:21:33,940 --> 00:21:35,820
They say that right before her death,

225
00:21:35,820 --> 00:21:37,580
this demoness even cursed her disciple,

226
00:21:37,580 --> 00:21:38,410
Su Yishui,

227
00:21:38,700 --> 00:21:41,060
with the Face-and-Heart Burning Curse.

228
00:21:41,130 --> 00:21:43,060
It was utterly humiliating.

229
00:21:43,290 --> 00:21:44,890
Her cruelty didn't end here.

230
00:21:44,940 --> 00:21:45,530
Mu Qingge

231
00:21:45,530 --> 00:21:46,820
merged her fate

232
00:21:46,890 --> 00:21:48,500
with the sovereign order

233
00:21:48,530 --> 00:21:49,650
of Wester Sect.

234
00:21:49,650 --> 00:21:50,460
If she dies,

235
00:21:50,650 --> 00:21:52,780
the disciples of Wester Sect will die!

236
00:21:53,140 --> 00:21:54,850
What a vicious demon!

237
00:21:55,020 --> 00:21:56,460
So Su Yishui had no choice

238
00:21:56,460 --> 00:21:58,260
but to find a Reincarnation Tree

239
00:21:58,290 --> 00:22:00,290
and a trace of her remaining soul.

240
00:22:00,770 --> 00:22:02,430
With half of his Golden Core,

241
00:22:02,460 --> 00:22:03,790
he helped her be reborn,

242
00:22:04,170 --> 00:22:05,830
in hopes that with her return,

243
00:22:06,020 --> 00:22:08,460
her curse on Wester Sect would be broken

244
00:22:09,160 --> 00:22:10,390
and she'd help him

245
00:22:10,410 --> 00:22:12,730
locate the missing Spirit Spring.

246
00:22:13,990 --> 00:22:14,990
Sovereign Su

247
00:22:15,010 --> 00:22:17,420
is such an upright and honorable man,

248
00:22:17,700 --> 00:22:19,630
yet he had to extend a demon's life.

249
00:22:19,940 --> 00:22:22,820
What an abominable pity!

250
00:22:23,170 --> 00:22:24,210
So how long

251
00:22:24,380 --> 00:22:25,290
does it take to

252
00:22:25,290 --> 00:22:26,730
resurrect that demoness?

253
00:22:26,730 --> 00:22:27,900
Eighteen years.

254
00:22:28,580 --> 00:22:29,460
Mu Qingge

255
00:22:30,210 --> 00:22:32,020
is coming back soon!

256
00:22:35,580 --> 00:22:36,440
Dear audience,

257
00:22:37,290 --> 00:22:38,610
the tales of Mount Wester

258
00:22:38,610 --> 00:22:40,210
will end here today!

259
00:22:40,870 --> 00:22:42,700
If you're worried that the demoness

260
00:22:42,700 --> 00:22:43,850
will harm the mortal world,

261
00:22:43,850 --> 00:22:45,200
why don't you get prepared?

262
00:22:45,200 --> 00:22:46,020
I have portraits

263
00:22:46,020 --> 00:22:47,870
of the righteous demon-slaying sovereign,

264
00:22:47,870 --> 00:22:49,700
Su Yishui, available for purchase.

265
00:22:49,700 --> 00:22:50,820
One cash for one.

266
00:22:51,020 --> 00:22:52,380
It'll subdue evil

267
00:22:52,380 --> 00:22:53,710
and keep your home safe.

268
00:22:54,140 --> 00:22:55,270
Anyone interested?

269
00:22:55,410 --> 00:22:56,580
Grab one while you can.

270
00:22:56,580 --> 00:22:57,290
Old Li.

271
00:22:57,580 --> 00:22:58,840
Who'd want to buy that?

272
00:22:59,270 --> 00:23:00,070
In my opinion,

273
00:23:00,260 --> 00:23:01,290
that man's so heartless

274
00:23:01,290 --> 00:23:02,620
for killing his master.

275
00:23:02,650 --> 00:23:04,090
He's no saint.

276
00:23:04,260 --> 00:23:06,920
-What are you talking about?
-Watch your words!

277
00:23:07,020 --> 00:23:09,350
Killing your master for justice is noble.

278
00:23:09,580 --> 00:23:10,340
Su Yishui

279
00:23:10,460 --> 00:23:12,500
will attain ascension sooner or later.

280
00:23:12,500 --> 00:23:14,700
Slandering him will bring you bad luck!

281
00:23:14,820 --> 00:23:16,150
You're the unlucky one!

282
00:23:16,260 --> 00:23:17,260
Ranran!

