571
00:39:28,780 --> 00:39:30,070
with an Incomplete Spirit Root

572
00:39:30,070 --> 00:39:31,130
who can't even withstand

573
00:39:31,130 --> 00:39:33,020
this little demonic energy from a secondary beast.

574
00:39:33,020 --> 00:39:33,740
She fell off the Tree

575
00:39:33,740 --> 00:39:34,850
before being fully

576
00:39:35,090 --> 00:39:36,020
nourished,

577
00:39:36,500 --> 00:39:37,760
so her heart's broken.

578
00:39:38,130 --> 00:39:39,780
It's a sign of premature aging.

579
00:39:39,780 --> 00:39:40,820
She is lucky that she's lived

580
00:39:40,820 --> 00:39:41,650
until now.

581
00:39:41,820 --> 00:39:42,580
If she dies,

582
00:39:42,580 --> 00:39:43,910
who can lift your curse?

583
00:39:44,340 --> 00:39:45,980
How about infusing her with power?

584
00:39:45,980 --> 00:39:46,500
I tried.

585
00:39:47,260 --> 00:39:48,660
I can't access her heart.

586
00:39:48,890 --> 00:39:49,750
Could it be that

587
00:39:49,850 --> 00:39:51,690
since she was your master in her previous life

588
00:39:51,690 --> 00:39:52,740
and your master-disciple pact

589
00:39:52,740 --> 00:39:54,470
was carried on to her next life,

590
00:39:54,720 --> 00:39:56,300
so you're not allowed access

591
00:39:56,300 --> 00:39:57,160
into her heart?

592
00:39:59,090 --> 00:40:01,340
The master-disciple pact is a blood pact.

593
00:40:01,340 --> 00:40:02,450
It can only be suppressed with another

594
00:40:02,450 --> 00:40:03,110
blood pact.

595
00:40:04,300 --> 00:40:06,680
Of the six pacts, the master-disciple pact is superior

596
00:40:06,680 --> 00:40:07,940
and never to be broken.

597
00:40:08,260 --> 00:40:09,130
In this world,

598
00:40:09,190 --> 00:40:10,130
what other blood pact

599
00:40:10,130 --> 00:40:11,370
could override it?

600
00:40:11,890 --> 00:40:12,620
There's one.

601
00:40:13,260 --> 00:40:15,060
Another master-disciple pact.

602
00:40:17,260 --> 00:40:17,780
Wait.

603
00:40:18,260 --> 00:40:19,220
You want to...

604
00:40:19,450 --> 00:40:20,690
Take her as my disciple

605
00:40:20,690 --> 00:40:22,350
to nullify the original pact.

606
00:40:24,610 --> 00:40:25,300
Guardian.

607
00:40:25,450 --> 00:40:27,450
Becoming the master of your master?

608
00:40:27,740 --> 00:40:29,170
It's such a bold

609
00:40:29,170 --> 00:40:30,220
and creative...

610
00:40:31,610 --> 00:40:33,570
and deviant method.

611
00:40:38,930 --> 00:40:39,530
Guardian.

612
00:40:39,690 --> 00:40:41,290
Why don't you reconsider it?

613
00:40:41,390 --> 00:40:42,650
There hasn't been such a precedent

614
00:40:42,650 --> 00:40:43,930
in the cultivation world.

615
00:40:43,930 --> 00:40:46,020
You've to endure the pressure of the laws of nature.

616
00:40:46,020 --> 00:40:47,150
I doubt you'd even be

617
00:40:47,220 --> 00:40:48,150
able to defy her.

618
00:40:49,450 --> 00:40:50,370
Besides,

619
00:40:50,870 --> 00:40:51,670
a lot goes into

620
00:40:51,680 --> 00:40:52,880
being a master.

621
00:40:53,980 --> 00:40:55,510
You've never been a master.

622
00:40:55,930 --> 00:40:56,660
Can you do it?

623
00:40:58,610 --> 00:40:59,470
Is it that hard?

624
00:41:00,820 --> 00:41:01,660
Since you've decided,

625
00:41:01,660 --> 00:41:02,940
let's return to Mount Wester

626
00:41:02,940 --> 00:41:04,000
and make it happen.

627
00:41:04,260 --> 00:41:04,890
Not yet.

628
00:41:05,260 --> 00:41:06,780
Her Fruit fell prematurely.

629
00:41:06,780 --> 00:41:07,710
She'll die instantly

630
00:41:07,710 --> 00:41:09,510
when she's too far from the Tree.

631
00:41:09,740 --> 00:41:11,410
She has never left Mount Absolute.

632
00:41:11,410 --> 00:41:12,340
Go to Mount Absolute

633
00:41:12,340 --> 00:41:14,340
and break off a branch from the Tree.

634
00:41:14,820 --> 00:41:15,680
One more thing.

635
00:41:16,240 --> 00:41:18,170
I can't confront Wei Jiu directly.

636
00:41:18,450 --> 00:41:19,710
Inform the Four Sects.

637
00:41:20,130 --> 00:41:20,690
Got it.

638
00:41:21,260 --> 00:41:22,850
Xue Ranran's Spirit Root is incomplete,

639
00:41:22,850 --> 00:41:24,450
but it's actually formless.

640
00:41:24,740 --> 00:41:25,410
She's like

641
00:41:25,410 --> 00:41:26,470
an Immortal Fruit.

642
00:41:26,650 --> 00:41:28,000
We mustn't let the Scarlet Sect get her.

643
00:41:28,000 --> 00:41:29,260
Formless Spirit Root?

644
00:41:29,780 --> 00:41:30,710
Immortal Fruit?

645
00:41:30,980 --> 00:41:32,640
She must stay in Mount Wester.

646
00:41:32,780 --> 00:41:33,300
Go on.

647
00:41:34,410 --> 00:41:34,760
Yes.

648
00:41:35,450 --> 00:41:37,250
So he didn't save me by accident.

649
00:41:37,500 --> 00:41:39,090
He's been targeting me.

650
00:41:39,610 --> 00:41:41,610
Just like the demonic cultivators,

651
00:41:41,780 --> 00:41:43,240
the Westers want to eat me!

652
00:41:50,690 --> 00:41:51,490
You're awake.

653
00:41:58,070 --> 00:41:59,660
Why are his face tattoos

654
00:41:59,690 --> 00:42:00,540
gone?

655
00:42:01,450 --> 00:42:02,250
What's wrong?

656
00:42:02,890 --> 00:42:04,020
Do I look very scary?

657
00:42:05,600 --> 00:42:06,430
No, no.

658
00:42:07,090 --> 00:42:08,130
Your profile is

659
00:42:08,220 --> 00:42:10,020
so gorgeous that I can't help but stare.

660
00:42:10,020 --> 00:42:11,480
It's far from being scary.

661
00:42:11,780 --> 00:42:12,240
Really?

662
00:42:13,150 --> 00:42:15,150
It's rare that someone's not afraid

663
00:42:15,220 --> 00:42:16,080
of my true face.

664
00:42:16,410 --> 00:42:17,540
It must be fate.

665
00:42:17,740 --> 00:42:19,340
I'll take you as my disciple.

666
00:42:19,610 --> 00:42:20,260
No, no.

667
00:42:20,690 --> 00:42:22,510
I have something urgent to attend to.

668
00:42:22,510 --> 00:42:23,890
You must've got the wrong person.

669
00:42:23,890 --> 00:42:25,090
It's definitely you.

670
00:42:25,170 --> 00:42:27,300
Born on September 9 in the Year of Qinggeng.

671
00:42:27,300 --> 00:42:28,910
You had a plum blossom mole on your face,

672
00:42:28,910 --> 00:42:30,740
which disappeared when you were five.

673
00:42:30,740 --> 00:42:32,870
You're destined with the Wester Sect.

674
00:42:34,540 --> 00:42:36,740
You're great at reading fortunes, huh?

675
00:42:37,420 --> 00:42:39,200
But the immortal path is too elusive.

676
00:42:39,200 --> 00:42:40,530
It's not the life I want.

677
00:42:40,740 --> 00:42:42,300
If you don't go up the mountain with me,

678
00:42:42,300 --> 00:42:44,090
you'll die of heart failure soon.

679
00:42:44,090 --> 00:42:45,500
Trying to scare me, huh?

680
00:42:46,220 --> 00:42:47,690
That's my fate then.

681
00:42:47,850 --> 00:42:49,500
You don't have to worry about it.

682
00:42:49,500 --> 00:42:50,580
Your life is mine.

683
00:42:51,220 --> 00:42:52,170
If I don't let you die,

684
00:42:52,170 --> 00:42:53,120
you can't die.

685
00:42:53,370 --> 00:42:55,020
Why are you forcing me?

686
00:42:55,410 --> 00:42:57,650
It's a Wester tradition to force discipleship.

687
00:42:57,650 --> 00:42:58,370
Back in the days,

688
00:42:58,370 --> 00:42:59,630
my master did the same.

689
00:43:00,130 --> 00:43:00,930
Is it that odd?

690
00:43:02,020 --> 00:43:03,620
Aren't you a righteous sect?

691
00:43:03,690 --> 00:43:05,650
Who said Mount Wester is a righteous sect?

692
00:43:05,650 --> 00:43:07,650
The Westers only follow their own way.

693
00:43:07,650 --> 00:43:08,850
Whether it's righteous or evil,

694
00:43:08,850 --> 00:43:09,710
we do as we will.

695
00:43:10,580 --> 00:43:12,220
This is the jade tablet of Wester disciples.

696
00:43:12,220 --> 00:43:13,400
You have to drop your blood into it

697
00:43:13,400 --> 00:43:14,080
and perform

698
00:43:14,450 --> 00:43:15,910
a discipleship ceremony.

699
00:43:17,370 --> 00:43:18,370
No thanks...

700
00:43:20,540 --> 00:43:21,600
The fortune teller

701
00:43:21,820 --> 00:43:23,820
said I'm born a jinx to my family

702
00:43:24,300 --> 00:43:25,220
and teachers.

703
00:43:25,580 --> 00:43:26,840
It's for your own good.

704
00:43:26,890 --> 00:43:28,690
Kneel and take me as your master.

705
00:43:32,260 --> 00:43:33,510
What's wrong with you?

706
00:43:33,510 --> 00:43:34,740
How can you get others to kneel?

707
00:43:34,740 --> 00:43:35,890
Will you kneel if I ask you to?

